OL,3,CPolice 'truly sorry' to family for
OL,4,Cshortcomings after prisoner's death
OL,6,FGuernsey's most senior police officer
OL,7,Fhas apologised to the family of a 39-
OL,8,Fyear-old man for shortcomings in
OL,9,Fcommunication following his death.
OL,11,FDarren Salituri was found deceased in
OL,12,Fhis cell at Les Nicolles Prison on the
OL,13,Fmorning of Monday 2 February, with
OL,14,Fthis information - including his name
OL,15,Fand age - released by the force to the
OL,16,Fmedia at 2pm the same day.
OL,18,FIn their statement, Guernsey Police
OL,19,Fsaid "the family of the deceased and
OL,20,Fthe victims of his offending" had been
OL,21,Fmade aware that morning.
