OL,3,CPolice 'truly sorry' to family for
OL,4,Cshortcomings after prisoner's death
OL,6,FHowever, ITV News has spoken directly
OL,7,Fwith Mr Salituri's mother on multiple
OL,8,Foccasions and she says the force
OL,9,Ffailed to tell her in an appropriate
OL,10,Fway that her son had died.
OL,12,FShe explains that while she was
OL,13,Finformed shortly after he was found
OL,14,Fdeceased, she was not given enough
OL,15,Ftime to tell other relatives before it
OL,16,Fwas released publicly.
OL,18,FChief Officer Damian Kitchen has now
OL,19,Fadmitted issues in the force's initial
OL,20,Fcontact with the family and the
OL,21,Fdetails they shared with them.
