OL,3,CPolice 'truly sorry' to family for
OL,4,Cshortcomings after prisoner's death
OL,6,FIn a statement, he explains: "In
OL,7,Fhindsight, it is clear that our first
OL,8,Fcommunication with the family didn't
OL,9,Fgive them the level of support they
OL,10,Fdeserved, the most accurate
OL,11,Finformation at the time, nor meet our
OL,12,Fown high standards, and for that, we
OL,13,Fhave apologised to them and are
OL,14,Fcommitted to doing better.
