OL,3,CPolice 'truly sorry' to family for
OL,4,Cshortcomings after prisoner's death
OL,6,F"I am truly sorry that we didn't
OL,7,Fprovide the best initial service and
OL,8,Fwill ensure that either I or a member
OL,9,Fof the senior team at Guernsey Police
OL,10,Faffords the family an opportunity for
OL,11,Fa personal meeting to reiterate this
OL,12,Fapology.
OL,14,F"Immediate actions were taken to
OL,15,Faddress their concerns, and this has
OL,16,Fbeen discussed with them."
