OL,6,FWhen Mr Kitchen took over the role of
OL,7,FGuernsey's Chief Officer in late 2024,
OL,8,Fhe stated his aim to build public
OL,9,Ftrust in the service and for the force
OL,10,Fto learn from its mistakes.
OL,12,FInvestigations into Mr Salituri's
OL,13,Fdeath are ongoing and it is not being
OL,14,Ftreated as suspicious.
